  (5, 'direction', 'D', 'Direction: Lacks a clear episodic vision, with no consistent theme or narrative direction and identity. Establish what the series is about and how each episode serves that core.'),
  (5, 'direction', 'D', 'Direction: Episodes are disjointed, failing to establish continuity or progression. Plan continuity and narrative progression across episodes at the series design stage — each episode must connect and build on the one before it.'),
